ee the article B&aacute;nh cuốn in the Vietnamese Wikipedia.<br /><br />A similar Chinese dish is the Cantonese dish coeng4 fan2 (肠粉; pinyin: ch&aacute;ngfěn), usually translated into English as "steamed rice roll" or "rice noodle roll," which is a form of dim sum.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '16:02:14', 1, 'admin');
